## 10.Testing

* Submitted multiple requests
* Verified approval flow
* Checked task assignment
* Confirmed status updates

---

## 11. Results

* Reduced manual work
* Faster request processing
* Improved tracking and visibility
* Efficient task management

---

## 12. Conclusion

This project successfully automates the network request lifecycle in ServiceNow.
It improves efficiency, ensures proper approvals, and provides real-time tracking of requests and tasks.

